# API Client Composables

## Objective
Create the frontend communication layer to fetch instance data from the Express backend.

## Tasks
1. Create `src/composables/useInstances.ts`.
2. Implement fetching logic pointing to the `VITE_API_URL`.
3. Define TypeScript interfaces for `TotemInstance` (e.g., `id`, `name`, `readmeContent`).
4. Support loading and error states within the composable.
